    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>free</strong> <strong>range</strong> <strong>chicken breast portions</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Dissolve <strong>half</strong> your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[450ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
