      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once thickened, add the <strong>chopped chicken</strong>,<strong> halved green beans </strong>and <strong>diced apricots</strong> to the pan</p><p>Reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for a further 12-15 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>Moroccan-style free range chicken</strong></p>",
