    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, add the <strong>lemon zest</strong>, <strong>remaining chicken stock mix </strong>and <strong>couscous</strong> to a heatproof bowl with a good grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Add 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> to the bowl, then cover and set aside</p><p>Fluff with a fork before serving</p>",
